<h2>Our Mission</h2>

<p><a href="http://www.brandonbruno.com" target="_blank">Brandon Bruno</a> created Sitecore Spark in 2016 to provide a new perspective on Sitecore education.</p>
<p>Sitecore Spark aims to be a comprehensive introduction to understanding the Sitecore 8 platform.</p>
<p>Sitecore concepts are be broken down into short, simple articles that are designed to be consumable in minutes and useful for developers of all levels. Sitecore Spark can be used as training material for new developers or quick reference for seasoned veterans.</p>

